Let me also check what the `ValidateCreate` and `ValidateUpdate` method signatures look like more carefully — they call `v.validate()` which already has the inline logic. The right approach is to refactor `validate()` to call `ValidateArchitecturesSet()` instead of the inline duplicate check.

